5D840590.Line1.FD852: You are the last visitor to my sanctum. Though you come too late, just as Lilith did before you.

A677DCA5.Line15.FD852: How we hurtle towards the prophecy’s end...

F7787F12.Line3.FD852: For it was my father, Inarius, who arrived here first. It unfolded as my visions foretold.
